description:
For more information on our upcoming campmeeting click this link: https://events.amazingdiscoveries.org/camp-meeting

Join us for our 2022 Camp Meeting August 15th to 20th, where you will be able to experience country living hands on! At this camp meeting we would like to give everyone an opportunity to learn practical skills to help prepare for the No Buy No Sell time period, prophesied in the book of Revelation. Come prepared to experience the country in its finest and learn how to live without power, how to garden, store food and more! Morning and evening will have a meeting where you will learn Biblical ways of Interpreting Prophecy, laying the foundation to help understand a lot of major prophecies in the Bible! This camp meeting will mimic some of our mission school content, so join to experience what the mission school will be like!
fulltitle: End-time Preparation Campmeeting Registration Now Open!
